      <p class="flag-discourse">Discuss on <a target="_blank" href="<%= flagpost_url %>">flagpost.nz</a> ». <span class="break-mobile"></span>View original submission on <a target="_blank" href="<%= submission_url %>" target="_blank">flag.govt.nz</a> »</p>
